can be work with document(JSON,XML)
Netflix, Hotstar use cloud database
PostgreSql - open source, ORDBMS, No hidden charge


Download - 
     1. sudo apt install postgresql
     2. sudo systemctl status postgresql - check if installed
Go inside postgresql -  sudo -i -u postgres
                     - \psql
                     - \l list all the databases (show databases;)
                     - create database customer (To create database)
                     - \c customer (To use Database)(connect to database)
                     - \dt (To list the tables inside the selected database) (show tables)
                     -// \d tablename (To describe the table)
                     - create table table name();  (same)
                     - 
                     - \q exit
                     - 
                     
                     
Data Manipulate Language:
            insert,update,delete
Data Definition Language:
            create,alter,drop,truncate,rename
                                 
                     






Note:
   1. column name in table is known as metadata
